146
01:05:39,433 --> 01:05:40,833
<b>flag and create a country.</b>

147
01:05:41,266 --> 01:05:43,599
<b>You need a permanent population, a</b>

148
01:05:43,599 --> 01:05:45,066
<b>functioning government, and</b>

149
01:05:45,066 --> 01:05:46,766
<b>recognition from other states.</b>

150
01:05:47,433 --> 01:05:50,866
<b>Berthawil has none of those. So legally,</b>

151
01:05:51,433 --> 01:05:52,900
<b>Emily is not a princess.</b>

152
01:05:53,633 --> 01:05:55,333
<b>But the Hinton story going viral,</b>

153
01:05:55,766 --> 01:05:56,666
<b>millions of views,</b>

154
01:05:56,933 --> 01:05:57,966
<b>hundreds of news outlets,</b>

155
01:05:58,333 --> 01:06:00,133
<b>that reveals something important.</b>

156
01:06:00,666 --> 01:06:03,633
<b>We're fascinated by the idea of unclaimed</b>

157
01:06:03,633 --> 01:06:04,966
<b>land, because almost</b>

158
01:06:04,966 --> 01:06:06,733
