159
01:06:07,500 --> 01:06:09,833
<b>Every piece of habitable land on Earth is</b>

160
01:06:09,833 --> 01:06:11,166
<b>claimed by some country.</b>

161
01:06:12,000 --> 01:06:15,733
<b>Except for Berthawil. Four small pockets</b>

162
01:06:15,733 --> 01:06:16,733
<b>along the Danube River.</b>

163
01:06:17,233 --> 01:06:17,966
<b>But that's a</b>

164
01:06:17,966 --> 01:06:20,133
<b>Croatia-Serbia border dispute.</b>

165
01:06:20,633 --> 01:06:21,566
<b>And parts of Antarctica.</b>

166
01:06:22,166 --> 01:06:24,699
<b>But the Antarctic Treaty System suspends</b>

167
01:06:24,699 --> 01:06:25,733
<b>all of those claims.</b>

168
01:06:26,533 --> 01:06:27,533
<b>That's it.</b>

169
01:06:28,166 --> 01:06:30,933
<b>In a world of 8 billion people divided</b>

