<b>touch because claiming it</b>

202
01:07:42,733 --> 01:07:44,066
<b>means giving up Khalaib.</b>

203
01:07:44,666 --> 01:07:46,000
<b>So when Jeremiah Heaton</b>

204
01:07:46,000 --> 01:07:47,733
<b>planted that flag in 2014,</b>

205
01:07:48,366 --> 01:07:49,866
<b>he wasn't just trying to make his</b>

206
01:07:49,866 --> 01:07:50,733
<b>daughter a princess.</b>

207
01:07:51,433 --> 01:07:53,333
<b>He was highlighting an absurdity.</b>

208
01:07:54,066 --> 01:07:56,733
<b>800 square miles of land between two</b>

209
01:07:56,733 --> 01:07:57,633
<b>countries that</b>

210
01:07:57,633 --> 01:07:59,066
<b>neither country will claim.</b>

211
01:07:59,633 --> 01:08:01,333
<b>Because admitting Berthawil is yours</b>

