<b>Everyone wants those territories.</b>

226
01:08:32,300 --> 01:08:34,566
<b>Berthawil is the only one nobody wants.</b>

227
01:08:35,300 --> 01:08:36,866
<b>That's not just a legal curiosity.</b>

228
01:08:37,466 --> 01:08:40,033
<b>That's a colonial border dispute that's</b>

229
01:08:40,033 --> 01:08:41,333
<b>still unresolved 70</b>

230
01:08:41,333 --> 01:08:42,633
<b>years after independence.</b>

231
01:08:43,399 --> 01:08:45,366
<b>And it won't be the last one.</b>

232
01:08:46,233 --> 01:08:48,366
<b>If this kind of evidence-based deep dive</b>

233
01:08:48,366 --> 01:08:49,833
<b>into historical oddities is</b>

234
01:08:49,833 --> 01:08:52,166
<b>your thing, please subscribe.</b>

